#, python-format
msgid "Element Builder: %(name)s"
msgstr "एलिमेंट बिल्डर: %(name)s"

msgid "List custom elements"
msgstr "कस्टम एलिमेंट सूची"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Returns all active custom elements for the store.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Populate element selection dropdowns\n"
"- Display available templates for search results\n"
"- List custom elements in page builder element library\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            स्टोर के लिए सभी सक्रिय कस्टम तत्वों को लौटाता है। **उपयोग के मामले:** - "
"तत्व चयन ड्रॉपडाउन को भरें - खोज परिणामों के लिए उपलब्ध टेम्पलेट दिखाएं - पेज बिल्डर तत्व "
"पुस्तक में कस्टम तत्वों की सूची बनाएं **सत्यापन:** प्रशासक सत्र की आवश्यकता है\n"
"        "

msgid "Not authenticated"
msgstr "अनुमोदित नहीं"

msgid "Permission denied"
msgstr "अनुमति अस्वीकृत"

msgid "Create custom element"
msgstr "कस्टम एलिमेंट बनाएं"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Creates a new custom element.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Create new data-bound UI element from builder\n"
"- Programmatically add custom elements\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"\n"
"**Side Effects:**\n"
"- Element becomes available in page builder element library\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            एक नया कस्टम तत्व बनाता है। **उपयोग के मामले:** - बिल्डर से नए डेटा-बांधे "
"गए UI तत्व बनाएं - कस्टम तत्वों को कार्यात्मक रूप से जोड़ें **सत्यापन:** प्रशासक सत्र की "
"आवश्यकता है **प्रभाव:** - तत्व पेज बिल्डर तत्व पुस्तक में उपलब्ध हो जाता है\n"
"        "

msgid "Validation error"
msgstr "सत्यापन त्रुटि"

msgid "Get custom element details"
msgstr "कस्टम एलिमेंट विवरण प्राप्त करें"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Returns full details of a custom element including its structure.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Load element for visual builder\n"
"- Retrieve element configuration for rendering\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            एक विशिष्ट तत्व के पूर्ण विवरण लौटता है जिसमें इसकी संरचना शामिल है। "
"**उपयोग के मामले:** - दृश्य बिल्डर के लिए तत्व लोड करें - रेंडर के लिए तत्व विन्यास प्राप्त "
"करें **सुरक्षा:** प्रशासक सत्र आवश्यक है\n"
"        "

msgid "Element ID"
msgstr "एलिमेंट ID"

msgid "Element not found"
msgstr "एलिमेंट नहीं मिला"

msgid "Update custom element"
msgstr "कस्टम एलिमेंट अपडेट करें"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Updates a custom element's structure and properties.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Save changes from visual builder\n"
"- Update element metadata\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"\n"
"**Side Effects:**\n"
"- Clears cached renders for this element\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            एक विशिष्ट तत्व की संरचना और गुणों को अपडेट करता है। **उपयोग के मामले:** "
"- दृश्य बिल्डर से बदलाव सहेजें - तत्व मेटाडेटा अपडेट करें **सुरक्षा:** प्रशासक सत्र आवश्यक है "
"**प्रभाव:** - इस तत्व के लिए कैश रेंडर को हटा देता है\n"
"        "

msgid "Partial update custom element"
msgstr "कस्टम एलिमेंट का आंशिक अपडेट करें"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Partially updates a custom element.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Update only specific fields\n"
"- Toggle active status\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            एक व्यक्तिगत तत्व को आंशिक रूप से अपडेट करता है। **उपयोग के मामले:** - केवल "
"विशिष्ट क्षेत्रों को अपडेट करें - सक्रिय स्थिति को स्विच करें **सत्यापन:** प्रशासक सेशन की "
"आवश्यकता होती है\n"
"        "

msgid "Delete custom element"
msgstr "कस्टम एलिमेंट हटाएं"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Permanently deletes a custom element.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Remove unused elements\n"
"- Clean up test elements\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"\n"
"**Warning:** This action cannot be undone. Consider setting is_active=false "
"instead.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"            एक व्यक्तिगत तत्व को दीर्घकालिक रूप से हटा देता है। **उपयोग के मामले:** - "
"अप्रयुक्त तत्वों को हटाएं - परीक्षण तत्वों की सफाई करें **सत्यापन:** प्रशासक सेशन की "
"आवश्यकता होती है **चेतावनी:** यह कार्रवाई वापस नहीं की जा सकती। इसके बजाय "
"is_active=false रखने के बारे में सोचें।\n"
"        "

msgid "Element deleted"
msgstr "एलिमेंट हटा दिया गया"

msgid "List bindable models"
msgstr "बांधने योग्य मॉडलों की सूची"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Returns all models that can be bound to custom elements.\n"
"\n"
"Each model includes:\n"
"- `key`: Model identifier (e.g., \"catalog.Product\")\n"
"- `label`: Human-readable name\n"
"- `icon`: Font Awesome icon class\n"
"- `fields`: Available fields with type info\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Populate model selector in element builder\n"
"- Get available fields for binding UI\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Returns all models that can be bound to custom elements.\n"
"\n"
"Each model includes:\n"
"- `key`: Model identifier (e.g., \"catalog.Product\")\n"
"- `label`: Human-readable name\n"
"- `icon`: Font Awesome icon class\n"
"- `fields`: Available fields with type info\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Populate model selector in element builder\n"
"- Get available fields for binding UI\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "

msgid "Dictionary of bindable models with their fields"
msgstr "बांधने योग्य मॉडलों का शब्दकोश उनके क्षेत्र के साथ"

msgid "List thumbnail presets"
msgstr "थंबनेल प्रीसेट सूची"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Returns available image size presets for thumbnail selection.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Populate thumbnail size dropdown when binding image fields\n"
"- Show available sizes in visual builder\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Returns available image size presets for thumbnail selection.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Populate thumbnail size dropdown when binding image fields\n"
"- Show available sizes in visual builder\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "

msgid "Add element to custom element tree"
msgstr "एलिमेंट को कस्टम एलिमेंट ट्री में जोड़ें"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Creates a new page_builder Element and adds it to the custom element's "
"tree.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Add elements in visual builder\n"
"- Build custom element structure\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Creates a new page_builder Element and adds it to the custom element's "
"tree.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Add elements in visual builder\n"
"- Build custom element structure\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "

msgid "Element created"
msgstr "एलिमेंट बना"

msgid "Custom element or parent not found"
msgstr "कस्टम एलिमेंट या पेड़ नहीं मिला"

msgid "Update element in custom element tree"
msgstr "कस्टम एलिमेंट ट्री में एलिमेंट अपडेट करें"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Updates an element's content or properties in the custom element tree.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Edit element content in visual builder\n"
"- Update element order\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Updates an element's content or properties in the custom element tree.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Edit element content in visual builder\n"
"- Update element order\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "

msgid "Element updated"
msgstr "एलिमेंट अपडेट कर दिया गया"

msgid "Delete element from custom element tree"
msgstr "कस्टम एलिमेंट ट्री से एलिमेंट हटाएं"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Removes an element and its children from the custom element tree.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Delete elements in visual builder\n"
"- Clean up unused elements\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Removes an element and its children from the custom element tree.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Delete elements in visual builder\n"
"- Clean up unused elements\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "

msgid "Set element binding"
msgstr "एलिमेंट बांध लें"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Creates or updates a data binding for an element.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Bind element content field to model field\n"
"- Configure thumbnail presets for image bindings\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Creates or updates a data binding for an element.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Bind element content field to model field\n"
"- Configure thumbnail presets for image bindings\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "

msgid "Binding saved"
msgstr "बांधन बचाया गया"

msgid "Clear all bindings for a custom element"
msgstr "एक कस्टम एलिमेंट के लिए सभी बांध खाली करें"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Deletes all element bindings for a custom element.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Clear bindings when changing target model\n"
"- Reset element to static content\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Deletes all element bindings for a custom element.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Clear bindings when changing target model\n"
"- Reset element to static content\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "

msgid "All bindings cleared"
msgstr "सभी बांधन साफ कर दिए गए"

msgid "Custom element not found"
msgstr "कस्टम एलिमेंट नहीं मिला"

msgid "Get page builder element primitives"
msgstr "पेज बिल्डर तत्व मूल तत्व प्राप्त करें"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Returns available page_builder element types for building custom elements.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Populate element picker in visual builder\n"
"- Get element configuration for rendering\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Returns available page_builder element types for building custom elements.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Populate element picker in visual builder\n"
"- Get element configuration for rendering\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "

msgid "List of element types with config"
msgstr "एलिमेंट प्रकारों की सूची जिसमें विन्यास है"

msgid "Get element configuration"
msgstr "तत्व विन्यास प्राप्त करें"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Returns full config.json data for a specific element type.\n"
"\n"
"Includes tabs, properties, base_properties for PropertyRenderer "
"integration.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Load element config for PropertyRenderer in visual builder\n"
"- Get property definitions for element editing\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Returns full config.json data for a specific element type.\n"
"\n"
"Includes tabs, properties, base_properties for PropertyRenderer "
"integration.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Load element config for PropertyRenderer in visual builder\n"
"- Get property definitions for element editing\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "

msgid "Element type identifier (e.g., \"heading\", \"image\", \"container\")"
msgstr "एलिमेंट प्रकार पहचानकर्ता (उदा., \"heading\", \"image\", \"container\")"

msgid "Element configuration with tabs and properties"
msgstr "तत्व विन्यास जिसमें टैब और गुण होते हैं"

msgid "Element type not found"
msgstr "तत्व प्रकार नहीं मिला"

msgid "Apply container layout preset"
msgstr "कंटेनर लेआउट प्रीसेट लागू करें"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Applies a layout preset to a container element, creating child columns.\n"
"\n"
"**Available Layouts:**\n"
"- `full-width`: Single full-width column\n"
"- `2-equal`: Two equal columns (50/50)\n"
"- `2-col-33-66`: 1/3 + 2/3 columns\n"
"- `2-col-66-33`: 2/3 + 1/3 columns\n"
"- `3-equal`: Three equal columns\n"
"- `3-col-25-50-25`: 1/4 + 1/2 + 1/4 columns\n"
"- `4-equal`: Four equal columns\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Initialize a container with a column layout\n"
"- Set up multi-column layouts in custom elements\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Applies a layout preset to a container element, creating child columns.\n"
"\n"
"**Available Layouts:**\n"
"- `full-width`: Single full-width column\n"
"- `2-equal`: Two equal columns (50/50)\n"
"- `2-col-33-66`: 1/3 + 2/3 columns\n"
"- `2-col-66-33`: 2/3 + 1/3 columns\n"
"- `3-equal`: Three equal columns\n"
"- `3-col-25-50-25`: 1/4 + 1/2 + 1/4 columns\n"
"- `4-equal`: Four equal columns\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Initialize a container with a column layout\n"
"- Set up multi-column layouts in custom elements\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "

msgid "Layout applied successfully"
msgstr "लेआउट सफलतापूर्वक लागू कर दिया गया"

msgid "Invalid layout type"
msgstr "अमान्य लेआउट प्रकार"

msgid "Move element to new parent/position"
msgstr "एलिमेंट को नए पेरेंट/स्थान पर ले जाएं"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Moves an element to a new parent container and/or position.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Reorder elements via drag-and-drop\n"
"- Move elements between containers\n"
"- Re-parent elements in the tree\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Moves an element to a new parent container and/or position.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Reorder elements via drag-and-drop\n"
"- Move elements between containers\n"
"- Re-parent elements in the tree\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "

msgid "Element moved successfully"
msgstr "एलिमेंट सफलतापूर्वक ले जा दिया गया"

msgid "Element or parent not found"
msgstr "एलिमेंट या पेरेंट पाया नहीं गया"

msgid "Render element preview"
msgstr "एलिमेंट पूर्वावलोकन रेंडर करें"

msgid ""
"\n"
"Renders an element from the custom element tree as HTML for visual preview.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Display visual preview of elements in the builder canvas\n"
"- Preview custom element with bound data\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Renders an element from the custom element tree as HTML for visual preview.\n"
"\n"
"**Use Cases:**\n"
"- Display visual preview of elements in the builder canvas\n"
"- Preview custom element with bound data\n"
"\n"
"**Authentication:** Admin session required\n"
"    "

msgid "Custom element ID"
msgstr "कस्टम एलिमेंट ID"

msgid "Element ID to render (optional - renders root if not provided)"
msgstr ""
"रेंडर करने के लिए एलिमेंट आईडी (वैकल्पिक - यदि प्रदान नहीं किया गया है तो मूल रेंडर करें)"

msgid "Rendered HTML preview"
msgstr "रेंडर किया गया HTML पूर्वावलोकन"

msgid "Element Builder"
msgstr "एलिमेंट बिल्डर"

msgid "Name"
msgstr "नाम"

msgid "Display name for the custom element"
msgstr "कस्टम तत्व के लिए प्रदर्शन नाम"

msgid "Slug"
msgstr "स्लग"

msgid "URL-friendly identifier"
msgstr "URL-अनुकूल पहचानकर्ता"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "विवरण"

msgid "Optional description of what this element displays"
msgstr "इस तत्व के द्वारा क्या प्रदर्शित किया जाता है, यह वैकल्पिक विवरण है"

msgid ""
"Model to bind data from (e.g., \"catalog.Product\"). Leave empty for static "
"elements."
msgstr ""
"डेटा बांधने के लिए मॉडल (उदाहरण के लिए, \"catalog.Product\"). स्थैतिक तत्वों के लिए "
"खाली छोड़ दें।"

msgid "Root element of the custom element tree"
msgstr "कस्टम तत्व वृक्ष का मूल तत्व"

msgid "Font Awesome icon class"
msgstr "फॉंट अवेज़ आइकॉन क्लास"

msgid "Category"
msgstr "श्रेणी"

msgid "Category for grouping in element library"
msgstr "तत्व पुस्तकालय में समूहीकरण के लिए श्रेणी"

msgid "Active"
msgstr "सक्रिय"

msgid "Whether this element is available for use"
msgstr "क्या यह तत्व उपयोग के लिए उपलब्ध है"

msgid "Created"
msgstr "बनाया गया"

msgid "Updated"
msgstr "अपडेट किया गया"

msgid "Custom Element"
msgstr "कस्टम एलिमेंट"

msgid "Element"
msgstr "एलिमेंट"

msgid "Content Field"
msgstr "कंटेंट फील्ड"

msgid "Element content field to bind data to (e.g., \"text\", \"src\")"
msgstr "डेटा को बांधने के लिए तत्व के सामग्री क्षेत्र (उदाहरण के लिए, \"text\", \"src\")"

msgid "Model Field"
